<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (dh wʿdk lyã hạtkẖbyny .. mn ywm ạlsẖr wtnjyny
 tmlk ʿly̱ qlby wʿly̱ ạ̉fkạry .. wjwh ḥḍnk hạtdfyny)2
 1- (qlt ly ạ̉msẖy ʿ ạlmyẗ msẖyt mʿạk .. ʿynk ʿlyã wsṭ ạlạ̉mwạj
 ạ̹ymạny ḍʿyf lkn fyk ạlạ̉mạn)2
 2- (qlt ly mgẖfwrẗ lk kẖṭạyạk .. wfyt ly bdmk kl ạlly fạt
 bdlt ḥzny bạ̉frạḥ smạk)2
 3- (qlby hạygẖny byk frḥạn .. hạ̉ʿln mjdk fy kl mkạn
 wạ̉sẖhd ʿnk kl ạlạ̉yạm)2</lyrics>
